element_texts.text:
Dear Bob,
You are a terribly funny inconsistent creature sometimes. Of course you are all right. I love you a lot and it doesn't make any difference. 
You love to scold me. You scold me if I do not take the children away from C and if I do. You pass horrible judgements on me, [unclear] me if [unclear] my ship is gaining air, sometimes where it is most in the open sea.
And through it all you
